TITLE: Installing googlethis with NPM
DESCRIPTION: This command installs the latest version of the googlethis package using the Node Package Manager (NPM). It adds the module to your project's dependencies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/luanrt/google-this/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm install googlethis@latest
```

