TITLE: Installing googlethis with Yarn
DESCRIPTION: This command installs the latest version of the googlethis package using Yarn, another popular Node.js package manager. It's an alternative to npm install.
SOURCE: https://github.com/luanrt/google-this/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
yarn add googlethis@latest
```

